      "raceComments": "{\"comment\":\"2. PHANTOM CARAT showed little early speed at her last couple, the latest finishing fourth (22.96) in a Grade 6 at Murray Bridge. Solid record at the distance winning three races. Better than last start and worth following up. 1. SEBON DIVA was well in the market last time but only managed fourth (20.58), beaten 6 lengths. Was in the money the start prior. Expected to give a good account. 4. GOLDEN ZEAL slotted in just off the lead from the wide draw last start and boxed on to finish third (20.19) at Angle Park in a Other over 342m. Expecting another good run. 8. LOCKABA ROCKET should be thereabouts despite an unplaced run here most recently.\",\"runners\":[2,1,4,8],\"exclusive\":false}",
